## FVWM Config File
# Joe's FVWM Config
# This configuration is intended to be usable in both moused and mouseless environments.
# To that end it makes heavy use of keyboard-commands, including vim-like movement.
#
# Global Settings
# Virtual Desktops are each the size of a single screen. No viewporting.
DesktopSize 1x1
EwmhNumberOfDesktops 4
EdgeThickness 1
ClickTime 400
MoveThreshold 10
Style * SloppyFocus, MouseFocusClickRaises
Style * PositionPlacement UnderMouse
# screen edges in form lrtb
EwmhBaseStruts 0 0 0 0
SnapAttraction 10 Screen
Style * NoTitle
Style * DontRaiseTransient, DontLowerTransient, StackTransientParent
Style * GrabFocusOff
Style * BorderWidth 1, HandleWidth 1

# Coloursets - defined colours can be found with '''showrgb | less'''
# Colours taken from the solarized theme be E. Schoonover
Colorset 0 fg rgb:26/8b/d2, bg rgb:07/36/42

Style * NoIconTitle

# Other Files called by this configuration
Read menu

## Functions
# Startup Functions - currently there is no startup function
#DestroyFunc StartFunction
#AddToFunc   StartFunction

# Complex Functions
DestroyFunc ShowDesktop
AddToFunc   ShowDesktop
+ I All (CurrentPage, Iconic, State 1) RestoreDesktop
+ I TestRc (Match) Break
+ I All (CurrentPage, !Iconic, !State 1) ThisWindow State 1 True
+ I All (CurrentPage, !Iconic, State 1) Iconify

DestroyFunc RestoreDesktop
AddToFunc   RestoreDesktop
+ I All (CurrentPage, Iconic, State 1) Iconify off
+ I All (CurrentPage, State 1) ThisWindow State 1 False

DestroyFunc FvwmTileHorz
AddToFunc   FvwmTileHorz
+ I Maximize false
+ I Maximize 100 50
+ I Move keep 0
+ I Next Maximize false
+ I Next Maximize 100 50
+ I Next Move keep -0

DestroyFunc FvwmTileVert
AddToFunc   FvwmTileVert
+ I Maximize false
+ I Maximize 50 100
+ I Move 0 keep
+ I Next Maximize false
+ I Next Maximize 50 100
+ I Next Move -0 keep

DestroyFunc FvwmCentre
AddToFunc   FvwmCentre
+ I Maximize false
+ I Maximize 50 50
+ I Move 50-50w 50-50w

DestroyFunc MoveNorth
AddToFunc MoveNorth
+ I Move keep 0
+ I WarpToWindow 50 50

DestroyFunc MoveSouth
AddToFunc MoveSouth
+ I Move keep -20p
+ I WarpToWindow 50 50

DestroyFunc MoveEast
AddToFunc MoveEast
+ I Move -0 keep
+ I WarpToWindow 50 50

DestroyFunc MoveWest
AddToFunc MoveWest
+ I Move 0 keep
+ I WarpToWindow 50 50

DestroyFunc NextRaise
AddToFunc NextRaise
+ I Next (CurrentPage !ButtonDocks) Focus
+ I Current (*) Raise
+ I Iconify false

DestroyFunc NextRaise
AddToFunc NextRaise
+ I Prev (CurrentPage !ButtonDocks) Focus
+ I Current (*) Raise
+ I Iconify false

DestroyFunc HoldToMove
AddToFunc HoldToMove
+ M Move
+ H Move
+ C Move

DestroyFunc AeroSnapVert
AddToFunc AeroSnapVert
+ I Maximize False
+ I Maximize 50 100

DestroyFunc AeroSnapHorz
AddToFunc AeroSnapHorz
+ I Maximize False
+ I Maximize 100 50

DestroyFunc HoldToResize
AddToFunc HoldToResize
+ M Resize
+ H Resize
+ C Resize

# Launching Programs
DestroyFunc FvwmViewManPage
AddToFunc   FvwmViewManPage
+ I Exec exec x-terminal-emulator -n "Manual Page - $0" -T "Manual Page - $0" -e man "$0"

## Key- and Mouse-Bindings
# Keys - Menus:
Key Menu A N Menu RootMenu
Key Menu A 1 Menu FvwmWindowOpsMenu 
Key Tab A 1 NextRaise
Key Tab A S1 PrevRaise
Key Menu A 4 WindowList Root c c 
Key p A 1 Exec exec /usr/bin/dmenu_run
Key p A S1 Exec exec /home/joe/scripts/dmenufm

# Keys - FVWM
Key q A S1 Quit
Key r A S1 Restart
Key q A Exec exec slock
Key x A Exec exec cb-exit

# Keys - Virtual Desktops
Key Right A 1 GotoDesk 1 0 3
Key Left A 1 GotoDesk -1 0 3
Key 1 A 1 GotoDesk 0 0
Key 2 A 1 GotoDesk 0 1
Key 3 A 1 GotoDesk 0 2
Key 4 A 1 GotoDesk 0 3
Key 1 A S1 MovetoDesk 0 0
Key 2 A S1 MovetoDesk 0 1
Key 3 A S1 MovetoDesk 0 2
Key 4 A S1 MovetoDesk 0 3

# Keys - WM
Key c WFS S1 Close
Key n WTFS 1 Maximize
Key m A 1 Iconify
Key d A 1 ShowDesktop
Key minus WTFS 1 FvwmTileHorz
Key semicolon WTFS 1 FvwmTileVert
Key h WFS 1 MoveWest
Key j WFS 1 MoveSouth
Key k WFS 1 MoveNorth
Key l WFS 1 MoveEast
Key Home WFS 1 FvwmCentre

# Keys - Applications
Key Return A 1 Exec exec x-terminal-emulator
Key w A 4 Exec exec iceweasel
Key e A 4 Exec exec gvim
Key f A 4 Exec exec pcmanfm
Key t A 4 Exec exec x-terminal-emulator
Key m A 4 Exec exec rhythmbox
Key v A 4 Exec exec gnome-mplayer
Key q A 4 Exec exec slock

# Mouse:
Mouse 3 R A Menu RootMenu
Mouse 1 R A Menu FvwmWindowOpsMenu
Mouse 2 R A WindowList
Mouse 1 WFS 1 pick HoldToMove
Mouse 1 I A Iconify
Mouse 2 I A HoldToMove
Mouse 3 I A Close
Mouse 3 WFS 1 HoldToResize
Mouse 4 R A Desk 1
Mouse 5 R A Desk -1
Mouse 1 WFS EdgeCommand West AeroSnapVert
Mouse 1 WFS EdgeCommand East AeroSnapVert
Mouse 1 WFS EdgeCommand North AeroSnapHorz
Mouse 1 WFS EdgeCommand South AeroSnapHorz
